3D&h=deeca663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/sebe2fkq</a> <br />\n(7.21)(23.24)示威者<span style=\"color: red;\">疑中槍倒地</span> 同伴築防線助急救<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/pmg9i1vt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fpmg9i1vt&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=d2d933d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/pmg9i1vt</a> <br />\n(7.21)（23:10）有示威者站在警方防線前用身體阻擋催淚彈，在<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有作出任何攻擊下突然被警察拉走</span>，警察更<span style=\"color: red;\">阻止記者上前拍攝</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/xkkjcdf1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fxkkjcdf1&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=55be2c6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/xkkjcdf1</a> <br />\n(721)警方施放催淚彈後，現場煙霧瀰漫，防暴警察更在濃煙中用警棍毆打示威者。<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/nq6ia5ue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fnq6ia5ue&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=c7c95a25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/nq6ia5ue</a> <br />\n(721) <span style=\"color: red;\">警察先主動進攻</span> 狂射催淚彈橡膠彈(CBC)<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/3wnsyqs5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2F3wnsyqs5&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=e76ca47c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/3wnsyqs5</a> <br />\n(721)(22:38 )在示威者推進途中，警方突然向人群射出催淚彈，及急速推進。示威者向警方投擲雜物還擊，警方再發射多枚催淚彈。<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/ns8i8iy7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fns8i8iy7&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=77723a07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/ns8i8iy7</a> <br />\n(721)(22:12) 港澳碼頭外，警察向示威者施放胡椒噴霧。(CBC)<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/tsdtd7zu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Ftsdtd7zu&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=aa52530d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/tsdtd7zu</a> <br />\n(721)(22:00) 干諾道西港澳碼頭外警察<span style=\"color: red;\">突然推進</span>。(CBC)<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/c46ztyj9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fc46ztyj9&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=8d150513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/c46ztyj9</a> <br />\n(721)(20:23) 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有委任證及證明文件</span>。(CBC)<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/spxgfu85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fspxgfu85&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=21f2d9b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/spxgfu85</a> <br />\n(7.21)(23:10)有示威者站在警方防線前<span style=\"color: red;\">用身體阻擋催淚彈</span>，在<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有作出任何攻擊下突然被警察拉走</span>，警察更阻止記者上前拍攝。<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/v1116l2v\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fv1116l2v&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=0610a13c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/v1116l2v</a> <br />\n(721)警察<span style=\"color: red;\">平射</span>橡膠子彈/煙霧彈 <br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/g641eu1x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fg641eu1x&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=9227e403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/g641eu1x</a> <br />\n(721)上環。<span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭者心聲</span>。他們有不想活的覺悟。<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/eejjvwug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Feejjvwug&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=02ea5937\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/eejjvwug</a><br />\n(7.21) 警方<span style=\"color: red;\">平射</span>開槍清場<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/mm56j9za\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fmm56j9za&d=gHNHb